"""
Pogo ↔ Discord bridge.

- Watches the human-mail directory and DMs the configured user when new mail
  arrives.
- Listens to DMs from the configured user; routes recognized commands to mg.

Configuration is read from ~/.pogo/bridget.env (key=value lines).

Required keys:
    DISCORD_BOT_TOKEN, DISCORD_USER_ID, DISCORD_SERVER_ID

Optional keys:
    MG_BIN           — full path to the mg binary (otherwise resolved on PATH)
    POGO_MAIL_DIR    — parent of new/ and cur/ (default: ~/.macguffin/mail/human)
    POGO_DESIGNS_DIR — directory containing mg-XXXX.md design docs
                       (default: ~/.pogo/designs)
    POGO_INBOX_REPO  — repo to file new ideas into via mg new
                       (default: ~/.pogo/inbox)

Tracks already-delivered mails in ~/.pogo/bridget.seen so a restart doesn't
re-deliver the entire backlog.
"""
